'''''The Voyages of the VSD Protector''''' was a [[holo-serial]] produced during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|time]] of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]]. It featured the exploits of the crew of the [[Protector (Victory I-class)|eponymous]] [[Victory-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory''-class Star Destroyer]], and its content was approved by the [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|Imperial Security Bureau]]. The program featured fictionalized versions of the dreaded [[Slivilith]]s as its primary antagonists.

